## Motion

| Token           | Value   | Usage                  |
|-----------------|---------|------------------------|
| `--dur-instant` | 80ms    | Micro-interactions      |
| `--dur-fast`    | 150ms   | Hover, focus states     |
| `--dur-normal`  | 250ms   | Transitions, toggles    |
| `--dur-slow`    | 400ms   | Accordion expand/collapse |
| `--dur-enter`   | 600ms   | Toast entrance, page enter |

**Easing curves:**
- `--ease-out-quart`: `cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1)` — standard exit
- `--ease-in-out`: `cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)` — standard transition
- `--ease-spring`: `cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)` — toggle, playful bounce

**Rule:** Always respect `prefers-reduced-motion` — disable all transitions and animations.

