## Components

### Buttons

**Base:** `display: inline-flex`, `border-radius: 9999px` (pill), `font-family: DM Sans`, `font-size: 14px`, `font-weight: 500`, `letter-spacing: 0.04em`. Active state: `scale(0.97)`. Focus: `outline: 2px solid var(--color-oro); outline-offset: 3px`.

| Variant       | Background             | Color         | Border                  | Usage |
|---------------|------------------------|---------------|-------------------------|-------|
| Primary       | `--color-obsidian`     | `#F0EAE0`     | none                    | Default CTA on light surfaces |
| Gold          | `--color-oro`          | `--color-obsidian` | none               | Highest conversion moments only |
| Secondary     | `white`                | `--color-obsidian` | `1.5px solid --color-bone` | Supporting actions |
| Ghost         | `transparent`          | `--color-obsidian` | none               | Tertiary, "Learn More" |
| Subtle        | `--color-parchment`    | `--color-siena`    | none               | Low-emphasis, "See All" |
| Destructive   | `#F5DEDE`              | `--color-error`    | none               | Cancel, delete actions |

**Sizes:** `btn-sm` (12px, 9px 18px), default (14px, 14px 28px), `btn-lg` (16px, 18px 36px), `btn-icon` (44x44px circle).

**States:** Disabled → `opacity: 0.35; cursor: not-allowed`. Loading → spinning border pseudo-element after label.

### Cards

#### Destination Card
- `border-radius: 20px`, `background: white`, `border: 1px solid --color-bone`, `box-shadow: --shadow-sm`.
- Hover: `box-shadow: --shadow-lg; transform: translateY(-4px)`.
- Image area: 220px height, with optional badge (pill, 10px uppercase, dark glass bg with gold text).
- Body: location eyebrow (11px uppercase terracotta) → title (Cormorant 22px/500) → description (13px #7A7060) → footer with price + stars.
- Price: "From" label (11px #7A7060) + value (Cormorant 22px/500).
- Stars: `color: --color-oro`.

#### Package Card (Horizontal)
- `grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr`. Image left, body right.
- Tags: pill badges (`tag`, `tag-luxury`, `tag-bestseller`, `tag-exclusive`).
- Title: Cormorant 28px/500.
- Meta items: "8 nights · 4 villas", "Private transfers", etc.
- Footer: price left, buttons right (Secondary + Gold).

#### Review Card
- White bg, bone border, radius-xl, padding space-8.
- Gold stars (16px) → italic Cormorant 20px quote → author (avatar circle 44px + name + location).

### Forms

**Input:** `padding: 14px 16px`, `font-size: 15px`, `background: --color-travertine`, `border: 1.5px solid --color-bone`, `border-radius: 8px`.
- Placeholder color: `#B5A890`.
- Hover: border `#C0B098`.
- Focus: border obsidian + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,23,20,0.08)`.
- Error: border `--color-error` + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(139,46,46,0.08)`.
- Success: border `--color-success`.
- Label: 12px/500 uppercase, `letter-spacing: 0.08em`, `opacity: 0.75`.
- Hint: 12px `#7A7060`. Error message: 12px `--color-error` with icon.

**Select:** Same base as input + custom chevron SVG background-image at `right 16px center`.

**Typebox (inline text field):** Used in search bars and destination fields where the value is user-typed. Same label pattern as search bar fields: 10px/600 uppercase, `letter-spacing: 0.16em`, `--color-terracotta`. Input: borderless, transparent background, `font-size: 15px`, `font-weight: 500` when filled, color `--color-obsidian`; placeholder `#B5A890`. Container: same padding and layout as other search bar fields (e.g. `p-4`), receives hover/focus/selected states (bone bg when selected, focus ring oro). No inner input border; focus ring on the container or `outline: none` on input with container focus-visible. Min width for comfortable tap target. Use `autocomplete` and `aria-label` for accessibility.

**Traveler Selector:** Bordered container with rows (label + sublabel | -/count/+ controls). Counter buttons: 32x32px circle, bone border, white bg.

**Date Picker:** Parchment header with month/nav → 7-column grid. Selected: obsidian bg, white text. In-range: `rgba(26,23,20,0.08)`. Check-in: left-rounded. Check-out: right-rounded. Disabled: `opacity: 0.3`.

**Toggle:** 48x28px, bone bg (off) → obsidian bg (on). Thumb: 22x22px white circle, spring easing.

### Feedback & Alerts

**Alert:** `border-radius: 12px`, padding `16px 24px`, flex row with icon (20px circle) + content (title 14px/600 + description 13px).
- Success: green bg/icon/title. Warning: amber. Error: red. Info: blue.

**Toast:** Pill shape (`border-radius: 9999px`), obsidian bg, `#F0EAE0` text, `box-shadow: --shadow-lg`, 13px. Entrance animation: `translateY(12px) scale(0.96)` → `translateY(0) scale(1)` over 600ms.

**Badges:** 10px/600 uppercase, `letter-spacing: 0.16em`, pill shape, 4px 10px padding.
- `badge-luxury`: gold tint bg, bronze text, gold border.
- `badge-bestseller`: blue tint bg, adriatic text, blue border.
- `badge-exclusive`: obsidian bg, champagne text.
- `badge-limited`: warning-bg, warning text, amber border.

### Progress Steps (Booking)

5 steps: Select → Dates → Travelers → Review → Confirm.
- Circle: 36x36px, bone border, white bg, 13px/600.
- Active: obsidian bg, white text.
- Done: success bg, white checkmark.
- Connecting line: 1px bone (done = success color).

### Skeleton Loading

Shimmer animation: linear gradient sweep (`parchment → bone → parchment`) at 1.5s infinite. Lines: 14px height with `short` (40%), `medium` (65%), `long` (90%) widths. Block: 200px height, radius-xl.

