## Do's and Don'ts

| Do | Don't |
|----|-------|
| Use Travertine (`#F5F0E8`) as page background | Use pure white (`#FFFFFF`) as page background |
| Lead with Cormorant Garamond for display text (22px+) | Use Cormorant at small body sizes (<22px) |
| Use gold (Oro) for exactly ONE CTA per section | Use gold as a background color or decorative fill |
| Use `--space-16` (64px) minimum between major sections | Compress sections to fit more above the fold |
| Always pair color-coded alerts with text + icon | Use red borders as the only error indicator |
| Let the scroll be part of the journey | Prioritize information density over elegance |

